metadata.description:
In "sistemas.15" I am exploring the assembly of systems again. This time, a painting system that works with the definition and connection of points, movement, trace, color overlay, blendmodes, alpha control and a detailed choice of color pallets. The different canvas formats are intended to present different "angles" of the work. The humachine is painting thinks.

This project was developed using p5js.

Composition

- 2 Groups of palletes, 5 colors and 2 colors. Total of 43 palletes;
- 5 types of background colors;
- 4 Types of background textures patterns;
- 15 to 25 "connection points", that will connect lines, bezier, squares and ellipses;
- To save a png file, press S.

